                            <comment id="14460949" author="sormuras" created="Mon, 30 May 2005 00:25:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Aye! C=&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Configured via the above web.xml, the GroovyServlet reports:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;  strURI=&quot;/index.groovy&quot;&lt;br/&gt;
  scriptFilename=&quot;roovy&quot; (*** eek!)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;So, the wrong code is:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;        int contextLength = request.getContextPath().length();&lt;br/&gt;
        String scriptFilename = strURI.substring(contextLength).substring(1);&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;...which assumes quite a lot about lenght values.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
